{"tid":415780,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打熟運動手環, 可以入黎俾D意見?","createTime":"2017-09-27T09:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T01:42:12.000Z","uid":84307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"65af07de20cca08f1d89b5bd59c229b6285ab3ed","tid":415780,"uid":84307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:12:26.000Z","msg":"平時多數跑步/行山(有時游下水, 打羽毛球), 想買返隻運動手環track下GPS, 心跳, 即時速度, 距離等等<br />\n<br />\n個人偏好窄身, 手環型, 廢事太大隻唔舒服, 筆直$1000-1500左右<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我睇過下post, 見好多人都用Garmin呢個牌子, vivosmart系列好似幾岩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外, Samsung Gearfit 2好似都有類似功能, 睇落都ok<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打用過可以俾D意見, 或者有其他型號/牌子推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102d80ad12521e101a99a79859c095e60a488799","tid":415780,"uid":53794,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:12:49.000Z","msg":"apple"},{"pid":"0fd9b9e7dcacfb0b8c9a1f3b93db941c2e6de07a","tid":415780,"uid":57367,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:20:12.000Z","msg":"小米手環2 $199"},{"pid":"675d3a1909519fe2177067b215c879c7a527d608","tid":415780,"uid":84307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:56:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>apple</blockquote><br />\n用an機, 已經柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8defd79d6aa39813fd782938f7353923e9e338ac","tid":415780,"uid":84307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:00:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小米手環2 $199</blockquote><br />\n我始終唔係太信D大陸野, 之前留意過D其他淘寶手環, 平到一舊都唔洗, 仲成幾萬人買, 不過我覺得D數據會差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87681c43ca04789705c7cc45ff95a1abaf6b2dec","tid":415780,"uid":53578,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:49:52.000Z","msg":"自己用緊小米, so far唔錯<br />\n準唔準就唔知啦<br />\n另聽過fitbit呢個牌子 可以睇睇"},{"pid":"28abdadcb098090ee41a3727deb7208753e19588","tid":415780,"uid":84307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:37:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己用緊小米, so far唔錯<br />\n準唔準就唔知啦<br />\n另聽過fitbit呢個牌子 可以睇睇</blockquote><br />\n但我覺得小米比較似係智能手環, D運動數據有限, 無GPS, 即時速度果D功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dabfafce6a31bbf7821b9494fe42f7404a942e35","tid":415780,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:42:01.000Z","msg":"之前有實驗話屌米步數準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a45fa95eaa4c6ec4be16e141f166c6b1569e16","tid":415780,"uid":403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:44:38.000Z","msg":"vivosmart hr plus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1858e1666425eb79f42ff9f4b984164cc5721cbb","tid":415780,"uid":84307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>vivosmart hr plus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打係咪用過, 可唔可以講下用後感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d630574cd08c158871ff35f62e525768fb89d5","tid":415780,"uid":84307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:06:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前有實驗話屌米步數準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但我嫌佢無GPS同速度睇"},{"pid":"a3d1647ec4ff437bc7a43092a57dc4d05cff9113","tid":415780,"uid":84307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88e0892e58752b5eced1694fb01da2f38df